    "description": "<strong>Blood Sunset </strong> is an open-world, post-apocalyptic, survival RPG. You happen to find yourself on old deserted islands... full of zombies. You'll have to survive, kill, run away, get food, and resources.<br><br>Hunger, thirst, and death are the challenges you'll have to overcome.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br>*Driving cars<br>*Lots of zombies<br>*Friendly and enemy camps<br>*Building camps<br>*Big islands<br>*Hunting animals<br>*Crafting<br>*Points of interest with great resources, and with great danger!<br>*Gardening and farming with stages of growing plants<br>*Lots and lots of zombies<br>*Dive underwater and explore the depths to find more resources.<br>*Photo mode - create beautiful photos by pressing the L and K button<br><br><strong>Your main goal is to survive!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353660/extras/5da4676f57499db21ec8e42fe144ebfe.avif?t=1682716447\" width=480 height=168 /></span>",
